---
title: Veggie-Packed Chana Masala-Style Curry with Basmati Rice and Toasted Flatbreads
description: This dinner is perfect for any season ! Warm spices,  tender chickpeas  and oodles of veggies swimming in an aromatic sauce. Best thing, you don't have to choose between buttery naan or rice! You can have them both.
